{"id": 1138, "genre": 1001, "title": "对于团队讨论中的“头脑风暴”，你有什么不满？", "description": "Brainstorming, 听起来不明觉厉，其实不过如此。（题图来自：Lucas Wakamatsu）", "record_count": 3016, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160802155520YPekNV9Z1oEiFzS8.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-08-03T03:00:41Z", "options": [{"id": 104194, "content": "“风暴”过后的价值和意义是什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 701825}, {"id": 104213, "content": "要么没结论 要么变成领导的一人演讲", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 682076}, {"id": 104215, "content": "无限循环", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 674056}, {"id": 104216, "content": "开会时 没有一个好的 会议组织者 以保证 整整的风暴刮起来", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 700993}, {"id": 104218, "content": "总会有些思路清奇的人固执的坚持己见，坚决不接受他人的意见，最后独自不欢而散。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 701862}, {"id": 104219, "content": "就是谁都没想法，大家坐在一起互相伤害", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 700923}, {"id": 104221, "content": "呵呵", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 485679}, {"id": 104222, "content": "老板决策论", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1299330}, {"id": 104223, "content": "追求norm的多，追求truth的少", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 701872}, {"id": 104479, "content": "最后开始聊公司八卦?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 687677}, {"id": 104991, "content": "聊着聊着会吵起来", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 705005}, {"id": 104224, "content": "真正能够听人说话的参会者寥寥", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 681612}, {"id": 104225, "content": "一本正经胡说八道", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 658382}, {"id": 104226, "content": "一切没有充分事前准备的头脑风暴都是耍流氓", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 619094}, {"id": 104227, "content": "我只负责吃。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 622062}, {"id": 104228, "content": "都是抢着说话的，而抢着说的，都搞不懂他在说什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 606680}, {"id": 104229, "content": "反正只有自己在说话", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 701920}, {"id": 152359, "content": "会上说我没有想法。会散了背后比谁屁话都多。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 597341}, {"id": 104238, "content": "头脑风暴要出结果只能在几个有决策权，有脑子的人进行，人一多就是浪费时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 701932}, {"id": 104239, "content": "只有高手和精英凑在一起的头脑风暴才有用才不浪费时间，其他都是在扯淡罢了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 604114}, {"id": 104240, "content": "和一群傻逼谈风暴等于对牛弹琴", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 701958}, {"id": 105520, "content": "我宁愿选择有脑子的单独风暴", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 672607}, {"id": 104241, "content": "卡巴拉5", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 41883}, {"id": 104242, "content": "今天！在这！何尝不是一个各抒己见的风暴？点赞最高的一条也恰恰在说明着实情！哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 95996}, {"id": 104243, "content": "手头上还有很多事～ 能不爆了么～ ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 669561}, {"id": 104755, "content": "人云亦云、故步自封是头脑风暴的终结者，融合不同到一体方是出路", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 704146}, {"id": 104244, "content": "不如一言不合就跳舞?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 669561}, {"id": 104245, "content": "时不时还得跟zz解释", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 567978}, {"id": 104246, "content": "就怕不说话", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 702029}, {"id": 104247, "content": "太多废话", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 541330}, {"id": 104248, "content": "有时候会变成。。撕逼大会？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 702031}, {"id": 104249, "content": "风暴过去了就过去了，要总结要总结要总结…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 702027}, {"id": 104251, "content": "有什么好讨论的。大家很熟吗？有想法的人不屑于跟一群傻逼讨论。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 634366}, {"id": 104253, "content": "一般只有一两个人在说啊（´Д`）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 702123}, {"id": 104254, "content": "一般只有一两个人在说啊（´Д`）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 702123}, {"id": 104010, "content": "很容易冷场", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 699404}, {"id": 104011, "content": "越找参考创意越少", "image": null, "praise_count": 127, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 696587}, {"id": 104012, "content": "说着说着就跑偏了，有的人甚至从来不在一个调上。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 197, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 693160}, {"id": 104013, "content": "说着说着就扯远了", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 339512}, {"id": 104014, "content": "大部分讨论时间都被浪费 ?", "image": null, "praise_count": 175, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 532476}, {"id": 104015, "content": "就和今天的栏目一样，没人讨论呐", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 339512}, {"id": 104016, "content": "提出了比较好的点子老板也很赞赏然鹅实行时又因预算问题而作罢。", "image": "img/option/option/20160803112107xHbAPqzROGQgl0pj.jpg", "praise_count": 84, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 684257}, {"id": 104017, "content": "没有什么卵用还一直blabla。。。", "image": "img/option/option_pic/20160803112336fmgKtaPBYSc24HGvL.jpg", "praise_count": 56, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 690131}, {"id": 104018, "content": "永远都会歪楼", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 665738}, {"id": 104786, "content": "最后都成了八卦峰会", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 704727}, {"id": 104019, "content": "为什么会有这么蠢的游戏。大家很熟吗?️", "image": null, "praise_count": 82, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668850}, {"id": 104020, "content": "无论说什么最后都会因为预算被打回来，那让我们风暴个毛啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 538436}, {"id": 104276, "content": "不倾听他人的说话内容，只顾着抢着表达自己的想法。这样的人有严重的发言癖，要么是抢着说话，要么就是强忍着等别人说完，然后赶快说话，至于别人说了什么，压根没听进去。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 252898}, {"id": 107860, "content": "总有一个自我感觉良好的人不停的BB，根本不给其他人说话的机会", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 714437}, {"id": 104021, "content": "脑子有货的不说话，脑子有屎的一直叨叨，没脑子的都在叫好，最后还是靠boss一句话决策", "image": "img/option/option_pic/201608031129245j3AN0eJKSETfzy8O.jpg", "praise_count": 957, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 397696}]}